title: Obama says Democratic presidential candidates are optimistic
text: Photo: Jacquelyn Martin, AP President Barack Obama makes a "grumpy cat" face as he compared Republicans to the sad Internet cat while speaking to the Democratic National Committee 22nd Annual Women's Leadership Forum National Issues Conference in Washington, Friday, Oct. 23, 2015. President Barack Obama makes a "grumpy cat" face as he compared... WASHINGTON (AP) — President Barack Obama is trying to portray his party's presidential aspirants as optimistic and civil, while accusing the GOP's presidential candidates of being glum and divisive.
